{"tid":2297916,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「好詩分享」海子 - 面朝大海，春暖花開","createTime":"2020-11-23T15:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:40:07.000Z","uid":134739,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"273c9427a95c66516618a3efebf15c59d93aa586","tid":2297916,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"從明天起，做一個幸福的人<br />\n餵馬，劈柴，周遊世界<br />\n從明天起，關心糧食和蔬菜<br />\n我有一所房子，面朝大海，春暖花開<br />\n　<br />\n從明天起，和每一個親人通信<br />\n告訴他們我的幸福<br />\n那幸福的閃電告訴我的<br />\n我將告訴每一個人<br />\n　<br />\n給每一條河每一座山取一個溫暖的名字<br />\n陌生人，我也為你祝福<br />\n願你有一個燦爛的前程<br />\n願你有情人終成眷屬<br />\n願你在塵世裡獲得幸福<br />\n而我只願面朝大海，春暖花開"},{"pid":"ca2d2d57fcea6504348c3c5b1bb0a33141c13789","tid":2297916,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0826a79e89cce00fc778ddc2dca98e04294fabfb","tid":2297916,"uid":174171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"但可惜只有今天"},{"pid":"3b4a3eb69fe5b37079a0b0f96a8865f1c16a2168","tid":2297916,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"我懷疑樓主hack咗我部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係23號早上先google完呢句話意思。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdWTd1s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdWTd1s.png&h=1f70dd28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8070a979b8acc0f55d0ad9775cfb3f957930042","tid":2297916,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b4a3eb69fe5b37079a0b0f96a8865f1c16a2168","tid":2297916,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"我懷疑樓主hack咗我部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係23號早上先google完呢句話意思。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdWTd1s.png\" data-